  <?dbhtml dir="tabBar"?>
  <title>iOS toolkit tab bar</title>
  <para>
  	A <emphasis>tab bar</emphasis> gives people the ability to switch between different subtasks, views or modes in an app.
  	A tab bar is used to give users access to different perspectives on the same set of data or different subtasks related
  	to the overall function of an app. 
  </para>
  <para role="tip">
  	Please keep in mind that it is not possible to object map single tabs  within the tab bar but to object map the tab bar 
  	as a whole only. In order to interact with single tabs you have to use the according actions.
  </para>
